From: Delia Popescu <delia.popescu@enea.com>
Date: Tue, 12 Sep 2017 14:23:38 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Functest Dockerfiles with alpine image

Signed-off-by: Delia Popescu <delia.popescu@enea.com>
---
 docker/components/Dockerfile  | 2 +-
 docker/core/Dockerfile        | 2 +-
 docker/features/Dockerfile    | 2 +-
 docker/healthcheck/Dockerfile | 2 +-
 docker/parser/Dockerfile      | 2 +-
 docker/smoke/Dockerfile       | 2 +-
